article.description: — Kendric Davis scored 25 points as SMU beat East Carolina 71-56 on Monday.
article.headline: Davis scores 25 to carry SMU past East Carolina 71-56
article.linkText: Davis scores 25 to carry SMU past East Carolina 71-56
article.story: GREENVILLE, N.C. -- — Kendric Davis scored 25 points as SMU beat East Carolina 71-56 on Monday. Tyson Jolly had 11 points and six rebounds for SMU (11-4, 7-4 American Athletic Conference). Feron Hunt added nine rebounds. Jayden Gardner had 23 points and nine rebounds for the Pirates (8-8, 2-8). J.J. Miles added 11 points and six rebounds. The Mustangs improve to 2-0 against the Pirates for the season. SMU defeated East Carolina 70-55 on Dec. 16. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
